Package: Refinitiv
Type: Package
Title: Connect to LSEG/Refinitiv Eikon and DataStream from R
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Laurens van der Burg
Maintainer: Laurens van der Burg <laurens@ggbo.eu>
Description: R interface to LSEG/Refinitiv Eikon via direct JSON and to DataStream via the DatastreamDSWS2R package. This package is in no way affiliated with LSEG, Refinitiv, Eikon or Datastream. Use at own risk.
             This package makes use of the DatastreamDSWS2R package from CharlesCara on Github for DataStream Connections.
